name: Cookoo
body:
### Cookoo
Cookoo is a small device that reminds you when to turn off the gas for your pressure cooker. Keep it on your pressure cooker and forget about it. Cookoo will tell you when it's done cooking.

### Authors
Cookoo is brought to you by Sagar Gubbi and Dhruv Saxena.
